{"ID":"20240218161948-0w30de4","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"icon":"26f0-fe0f","id":"20240218161948-0w30de4","title":"1.1.5 \u0026lt;script\u0026gt; 标签","updated":"20240218162331"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240218162005-r3q3r20","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240218162005-r3q3r20","updated":"20240218162046"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当用户访问一个页面时，页面中包含的 JavaScript 代码会与其他页面内容一起传递给浏览器。"}]},{"ID":"20240218162055-obd380p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240218162055-obd380p","updated":"20240218162055"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在 HTML 里使用\u003cscript\u003e和\u003c/script\u003e标签，可以在 HTML 代码里直接包含 JavaScript 语句。"}]},{"ID":"20240218162059-cz43aho","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240218162059-cz43aho","updated":"20240218162149"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"aHRtbA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"\u003cscript\u003e\n  ...JavaScript statements ...\n\u003c/script\u003e\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240218162208-xe68z2j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240218162208-xe68z2j","updated":"20240218162208"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"本书的代码都是符合 HTML5 规范的，也就是说，\u003cscript\u003e元素没有任何必须设置的属性（在 HTML5 里，type 属性是可选的，本书的范例里都没有使用这个属性）。但如果是在HTML4.x 或 XHTML 页面里添加 JavaScript，就需要使用 type 属性了："}]},{"ID":"20240218162222-5d0zp01","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240218162222-5d0zp01","updated":"20240218162319"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"aHRtbA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"\u003cscript type \"text/javascript\"\u003e\n  ... JavaScript statements ...\n\u003c/script\u003e\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240218162328-1dhvadt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id"